<br>
Tudamorf: &quot;So? Are you claiming some sort of disparate treatment by the game server? Or the hardware perhaps? Maybe the routers have a little conspiracy going on ... &quot;ah, there's Scirocco's 'fire' packet, why don't I just uhh delay that a bit&quot;. :)&quot;<br>
