 The phrase is &quot;for all intents and purposes&quot;.  Sorry, just had to get that off my chest. ;)<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uscirocco.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Scirocco</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>FAQ/Index Moderator</span><br> <font color=#333399>(7/11/01 12:49:28 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Um</span><hr size=1> &gt;&gt;How can i, as a D&amp;D DM, have created enjoyable adventures where there was no player vs DM-controlled characters? <br>
