<br>
Size of the player pool.<br>
No screening for the player population.<br>
No accountability.<br>
Lack of serious consequences.  (A PKer getting killed by the APKers is NOT a serious consequence when the PKer is back in action in an hour or two.  Six months or so would be a different story.)<br>
